        "subject": "=No Recent Update on SubTask: {{$json.subtask_name}}",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #333;\">\n\n  <p>\n    Dear {{ $json.manager_first_name }} {{ $json.manager_last_name }},\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    We noticed that there has been no update on the subtask <b>{{$json.subtask_name}}</b> for the past <b>3 days</b>.\n  </p>\n\n  <h3 style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Subtask Snapshot</h3>\n\n  <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 600px;\">\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Subtask Name</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_name}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_description}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Current Status</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_status}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Priority</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_priority}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Last Updated On</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_last_updated}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Created On</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_created_at}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Start On</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_start_on || 'N/A'}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>End On</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.subtask_end_on || 'N/A'}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Responsible Person</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n        {{$json.responsible_person_first_name}} {{$json.responsible_person_last_name}}\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Project</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.project_title}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Parent Task</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.parent_task_title}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Milestone</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">{{$json.milestone_title || 'N/A'}}</td>\n    </tr>\n\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\"><strong>Subtask Link</strong></td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n        <a href=\"https://fm-matrix.lockated.com/vas/tasks/{{$json.subtask_id}}\" target=\"_blank\">\n          View Subtask Details\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n\n  </table>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n    Please review the subtask and update the status or add comments to avoid potential delays.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Regards,<br>\n    <strong>PMO – Task Governance</strong>\n  </p>\n\n</div>\n  </table>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 15px;\">\n    Please review the subtask and update the status or add comments to avoid potential delays.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Regards,<br>\n    <strong>PMO – Task Governance</strong>\n  </p>\n\n</div>",
